# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

## [0.1.4] - 2026-03-16

### Added
- Retry and exponential backoff for SourceForge requests.
- Reuse of a single HTTP session across requests.

### Changed
- Added polite delays between requests to reduce rate-limit errors.

### Fixed
- Better handling of HTTP 429 responses.

## [0.1.3] - 2026-03-16

### Added
- Initial stable importer version.